---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Clement Hoang">
  <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mb-10">Clement Hoang</h1>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink mb-12">
    <p>
      I'm a software engineer and builder, based in San Francisco. Currently at
      <a href="https://airtable.com" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Airtable</a>,
      leading agentic product development &mdash; an MCP server now live in the ChatGPT app store and as an
      <a href="https://claude.com/connectors/airtable" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">official Claude connector</a>,
      <a href="https://blog.airtable.com/superagent/" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Superagent</a>
      (an AI research agent), and an integrations platform connecting agents to hundreds of external services.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before that, I was tech lead at Credit Karma shipping consumer financial products to millions of users &mdash;
      identity monitoring, credit locking, and the Relief Center (a Fast Company World Changing Ideas finalist).
      At Meta, I contributed to React core and shipped
      <a href="https://legacy.reactjs.org/blog/2017/11/28/react-v16.2.0-fragment-support.html" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fragments in v16.2</a>
      &mdash; now one of the most widely used patterns in the ecosystem.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm fascinated by how AI is reshaping the way software gets built, how money moves, and how
      businesses operate. When I'm not shipping, I'm probably cooking something ambitious or playing badminton.
    </p>
  </div>

  <nav aria-label="Social links" class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
    <a href="https://github.com/clemmy" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://ca.linkedin.com/in/clementhoang" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://twitter.com/c8hoang" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://medium.com/@clemmmy" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Writing</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://instagram.com/professor.pan" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cooking</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="/coaching" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150">Coaching</a>
  </nav>
</Base>
